    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-03-22 09:46:38",
    "text": "I’ve an use case where data is pushed to nested hubdb tables via a custom CMS developed internally.\n\nFrom it anyone can update the slug of a page… but the menu is controlled by the advanced menu, so we have to edit the right column with the slug changes…\n\nSo an api to update the menu can help us, so the slug we change in a page can be updated also in the menu, and if someone forget to update it from HubSpot, it doesn’t broke the page"
  },
